  "name": "feature-timeline-agent-task-20260403-2324",
  "idea": "Feature: Timeline agent task creation from selected media. Enable the timeline agent LLM to create generation tasks (style transfer, subject transfer, scene transfer, combinations, image-to-video) using the existing create-task edge function. When the user selects images/videos on the timeline and gives instructions, the agent should: 1) Create a new shot containing the selected anchor images, 2) Call the existing create-task edge function to submit style-transfer, subject-transfer, scene-transfer, or image-to-video tasks based on user intent and selected media. The agent needs tool definitions and system prompt instructions explaining how to use these task types, what parameters they need, and how to create shots. Should reuse the unified task creation system already in the codebase.",
